skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: food holiday
des: Every day is a food-related holiday! Help us Celebrate Deliciousness with the Alexa Food Holiday Skill! Simply ask Alexa for the Food Holiday for today, or provide any date throughout the year, and she will tell you what food or foods are being celebrated on that day!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
